OL,3,CTaxis working out-of-area 'should be
OL,4,Cbanned to fix a broken system'
OL,6,FTaxi drivers should be banned from
OL,7,Fworking out-of-area to fix a "broken
OL,8,Fsystem", it has been claimed.
OL,10,FAfter it was revealed nearly half of
OL,11,Fprivate hire taxis in Greater
OL,12,FManchester are registered to a
OL,13,Fdifferent council, such as
OL,14,FWolverhampton, Mayor of Greater
OL,15,FManchester Andy Burnham began a
OL,16,Fcampaign to end the practice of
OL,17,Fdrivers operating in a region where
OL,18,Fthey are not licensed.
