OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F396A1757007425
OL,3,CTaxis working out-of-area 'should be
OL,4,Cbanned to fix a broken system'
OL,6,FThe mayor is meeting with key
OL,7,Fgovernment ministers on Thursday 4
OL,8,FSeptember, including the Transport
OL,9,FSecretary Heidi Alexander, to continue
OL,10,Fhis campaign as a law moves through
OL,11,FParliament which could stop the
OL,12,Fpractice.
OL,14,FMr Burnham said: "For too long,
OL,15,Fcommunities in Greater Manchester and
OL,16,Facross the country have been at the
OL,17,Fmercy of a broken taxi system that
OL,18,Fallows private hire vehicles and
OL,19,Fdrivers to be licensed hundreds of
OL,20,Fmiles away from where they live and
OL,21,Foperate.
OL,26,@vD@ROU
