OL,3,CTaxis working out-of-area 'should be
OL,4,Cbanned to fix a broken system'
OL,6,F"This is not just a matter of fairness
OL,7,Ffor locally licensed drivers to
OL,8,Fprotect their livelihoods ` it's a
OL,9,Fmatter of public safety.
OL,11,F"Greater Manchester has led the call
OL,12,Ffor reform, and it's great to see that
OL,13,Fbeing backed by our local MPs.
OL,15,F"With the government having already
OL,16,Faccepted Baroness Casey's
OL,17,Frecommendation regarding out of area
OL,18,Flicensing ` further reinforcing the
OL,19,Furgent need for change ` this Bill
OL,20,Fprovides an opportunity for decisive
OL,21,Faction to be taken by the Government."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOU}D@fO]
