OL,3,CTaxis working out-of-area 'should be
OL,4,Cbanned to fix a broken system'
OL,6,F"Avoiding unnecessary delay and acting
OL,7,Fquickly to address out-of-area
OL,8,Flicensing will allow us to restore
OL,9,Ftrust and raise standards through a
OL,10,Fsystem that is safe, fair, and locally
OL,11,Fcontrolled."
OL,13,FIt comes as Greater Manchester Labour
OL,14,FMPs Josh Simons, for Makerfield, and
OL,15,FJames Frith, for Bury North, supported
OL,16,Fthe cause for such an amendment in
OL,17,Fparliament as the bill received its
OL,18,Fsecond reading ` a move also
OL,19,Fpreviously backed by Liberal Democrat
OL,20,FHazel Grove MP, Lisa Smart.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@LO]
