OL,3,CTaxis working out-of-area 'should be
OL,4,Cbanned to fix a broken system'
OL,6,FMr Burnham has long hoped for the ban,
OL,7,Fand launched the 'backing our taxis'
OL,8,Fcampaign in April 2025, which changed
OL,9,Fhow Greater Manchester licences
OL,10,Foperated and called on the government
OL,11,Fto end out-of-area working.
OL,13,FThe campaign also asked ministers to
OL,14,Fextend VAT exemptions of taxis adapted
OL,15,Ffor disabled people, continue the plug-
OL,16,Fin taxi grant until March 2027, and
OL,17,Freduce the rate of VAT on public
OL,18,Felectric vehicle charging to 5%.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
