OL,4,Cbanned to fix a broken system'
OL,6,FA 12-week-long 'engagement exercise'
OL,7,Fwas launched on the same day, which
OL,8,Fhas now come to a close. It received
OL,9,Fmore than 5,000 responses from the
OL,10,Ftaxi industry.
OL,12,FTransport for Greater Manchester is
OL,13,Fnow preparing its recommendations for
OL,14,Fhow to change the areas of taxi
OL,15,Flicensing not covered by the English
OL,16,FDevolution Bill.
